# Travel Insurance System – Use Cases

This folder contains all Use Cases for the Travel Insurance Claim System.  

---

## List of Use Cases

1. [Submit Travel Insurance Claim](Submit_Insurance_Claim_UseCase.md)  
   - Describes the process for a customer to submit a travel insurance claim, including document uploads and confirmation.

2. [Register / Create Account](Register_Create_Account.md)  
   - Describes how a customer registers a new account on the portal.

3. [View Policy Details](View_Policy_Details.md)  
   - Describes how a customer can view policy coverage, limits, and effective dates.

4. [Approve / Process Claims](Approve_Process_Claims.md)  
   - Describes how insurance staff review, approve, or reject claims and notify customers.

---

## Notes
- Each Use Case includes a detailed flow, alternative flows, postconditions, and an ASCII flow diagram.  
- For updates, edit the respective Markdown file for that Use Case.

